buyExactEth(address,uint256).details: If less than `_minAmount` of tokens remain in the curve, the user will receive the remaining tokens

params._minAmountOut: Minimum amount of tokens to receive

buyExactTokens(address,uint256).details: If less than `_amount` of tokens remain in the curve, the user will receive the remaining tokensAny msg.value in excess of the actual cost will be forwarded to `_recipient`Maximum input amount is defined by msg.value

returns._0: Current price of the token, in wei of ETH per 1e18 wei of token

returns.active: True if the gauge is active
returns.closable: True if the gauge is closable
returns.currentPrice: Current price of the token, in wei of ETH per 1e18 wei of token
returns.eth: Total ETH paid into the curve
returns.target: Target amount of tokens to purchase

returns._0: tokensOut:  Amount of tokens the user will receive
returns._1: fee:        Fee that was subtracted from the user's purchasing power, in wei of ETH

returns._0: total cost: Amount the user pays, in wei of ETH
returns._1: fee:        Fee that was added to the raw cost, in wei of ETH

returns._0: tokensIn:   Amount of tokens the user will pay
returns._1: fee:        Fee that was added to the raw desired amount, in wei of ETH

returns._0: total proceeds: Amount the user receives, in wei of ETH
returns._1: fee:            Fee that was subtracted from the raw proceeds, in wei of ETH

params._maxInput: Maximum amount of tokens to sell

params._minAmountOut: Minimum amount of ETH to receive

buyExactEth(address,uint256).notice: Buy tokens with an exact amount of ETH, receiving as many tokens as possible

buyExactTokens(address,uint256).notice: Buy exactly `_amount` of tokens, paying whatever cost is necessary

ethPaid().notice: Total ETH paid into the curve

getCurrentPrice().notice: Get the current price of the token

getGaugeStatistics().notice: Get the current statistics of the gauge

quoteBuyExactEth(uint256).notice: Get the number of tokens which will cost `_amount` of ETH, inclusive of any fees

quoteBuyExactTokens(uint256).notice: Get the ETH cost of buying `_amount` of tokens, inclusive of any fees

quoteSellExactEth(uint256).notice: Get the number of tokens which must be sold to receive `_amount` of ETH, inclusive of any fees

quoteSellExactTokens(uint256).notice: Get the ETH proceeds of selling `_amount` of tokens, inclusive of any fees

sellExactEth(address,uint256,uint256).notice: Sell tokens for an exact amount of ETH, selling as few tokens as possible

sellExactTokens(address,uint256,uint256).notice: Sell exactly `_amountIn` of tokens to ETH

tokenTarget().notice: Target amount of tokens to purchase during the curve
